         <h2 class="text-center classname">新闻动态</h2>
       <div class="od mainContent">
       <h1 class="aTitle">降本增效，铸件自动化打磨设备</h1>
       <h2 class="articleTime">添加时间:2023-12-01&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>阅读次数:&nbsp;&nbsp;<script src="/index.php?c=article&a=hits&id=235" type="text/javascript"></script></span></h2>
       <div class="introduction nmt">
         <p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 目前在铸件打磨领域，随着劳动力成本和招工难度的不断上升，越来越多的铸造企业选择采用自动化机械设备取代人工打磨，<strong>自动打磨机</strong>带来的生产自动化和“机器换人”是其转型发展的关键所在。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/WNibia1NGwLkC0uhaeZutcvBxziaF9W1wib3ibhNAxlmRsH3vlglxgpTZxXAVnomT1x4fxxrYSNC2Uvu6AlpTrC9FIQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1"/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 利用<strong>自动打磨机</strong>淘汰高污染、高耗能、高成本的落后产能，也是深化节能减排，推动绿色工业升级的重要途径。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/WNibia1NGwLkC0uhaeZutcvBxziaF9W1wib3PRL3FWV39wqWb9K90nQ66h3Q1gyibcRJPp3PPT2e0rAiba0iadddeWkzA/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1"/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 而博恩科作为自动打磨领域的专业制造商，凭借与业内多家知名企业的合作经验，在设计自动化打磨解决方案时，通过更高效、更经济、更适合铸造企业的打磨方式发挥出功效，达到了行业提高生产效率、降低成本的目标。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/WNibia1NGwLkC0uhaeZutcvBxziaF9W1wib3jTCxg4A34qGGLhXzITvOCWn6AB7YoNlpwbU0ULOCOJk1mRpkrRF1Iw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1"/></p><section powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p><span style="text-wrap: nowrap;">&nbsp; &nbsp; ●博恩科自动化专注铸件自动打磨、自动切割等铸造后处理清理工序;旨在加快铸造企业智能制造步伐提升标准供给质量，解决铸造企业打磨环节从业人员短缺等问题。</span></p><p><span style="text-wrap: nowrap;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="text-wrap: nowrap;">&nbsp; &nbsp; ●通过自动化、数字化、智能化的自动打磨方式，更安全、更环保、更绿色、更低碳的解决铸件后处理的打磨难题。</span></p><p><span style="text-wrap: nowrap;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="text-wrap: nowrap;">&nbsp; &nbsp; ●为铸造企业降成本、提效率、保质量、减用工，实现打磨环节的转型升级，用数字技术、智能技术改造提升传统的铸件打磨方式。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 博恩科正顺应了这场机械化打磨革命，以丰富的应用案例为自动化打磨保驾护航，帮助企业达到降本增效的可持续发展。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/WNibia1NGwLkC0uhaeZutcvBxziaF9W1wib31CUVgggNFVJes5MdDVU19OYnYypxbb7vmAJNZCOHXIAoAXuia9mesQA/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 博恩科自动打磨机的专业性，已经在多种铸件自动化打磨应用中得到了证明：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/WNibia1NGwLkC0uhaeZutcvBxziaF9W1wib35qWfAyfPoVtiaXNeYIYMWQhQibIhFMXT3bGbrqg4h4e3OpibmAvB0E3Cg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/WNibia1NGwLkC0uhaeZutcvBxziaF9W1wib3NKbJyEricic6qG1ybgBzUad3pkXqPh3yp3n0p96TibQGVmqNsiaHiabh2yQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/WNibia1NGwLkC0uhaeZutcvBxziaF9W1wib3Bp56OjiaRWic8o3tBQqFalCj24VvUIqwZicuVpBtcGUeiaNIP8SYywQdNw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/WNibia1NGwLkC0uhaeZutcvBxziaF9W1wib3NjlBlS7pr8wQLGicnwia1ScgeZ4ujll79wc8mib5JJmbm36hjlwaAqa4A/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1"/></p><p><span style="text-wrap: nowrap;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 博恩科技术团队在自动打磨领域的技术创新，助推了相关产业的绿色转型发展和智能化升级，为从业人员创造更好的工作环境，贯彻了我们以人为本、持续发展的理念和责任。</span></p><p><span style="text-wrap: nowrap;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 未来，博恩科仍将迎合绿色发展趋势并结合自身优势，推出更多专业自动化打磨应用的产品和解决方案，以科技举百业，以创新利个人。</span><br/></p><p><span style="text-wrap: nowrap;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 如果您也关注自动打磨机的发展，欢迎与我们分享您在铸件自动打磨机方面的真知灼见，或者提出您的问题，博恩科专员会尽快与您联系！</span><br/></p><p><span style="text-wrap: nowrap;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p></section><p><br/></p>         <div class="od articlePages">
         <div class="text-right"><a href="/article/236.html">上一页:&nbsp;博恩科铸件自动打磨机器人：让打磨工作变得更简单、更高效！</a></div>         <div class="text-right"><a href="/article/234.html">下一页:&nbsp;解读“打磨”</a></div>         <div class="text-right"><a href="/article/type/12-1.html">返回列表</a></div>
         </div>
       </div>
